stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Create Flight Plan
    
    Draft --> Approved: Approve
    Draft --> Rejected: Reject
    Draft --> Superseded: Update (creates new version)
    
    Approved --> AssignedToOverpass: Assign to Overpass
    Approved --> Superseded: Update (creates new version)
    
    AssignedToOverpass --> Transmitted: Scheduler transmits to GS
    AssignedToOverpass --> Failed: Transmission fails or GS offline
    AssignedToOverpass --> Superseded: Update (creates new version)
    
    Transmitted --> [*]
    Rejected --> [*]
    Superseded --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
    